	Thanks for choosing Razorpay as Payment Gateway.

	Please follow below steps to configure Razorpay into your core php application
	1. Download complete folder
	2. Change razorpay api key and secret key in charge.php file and index.php file
	3. Create a database(if you dont have) and import corephp.sql file using PHPMyadmin
	4. Now tried to do a sameple transaction
	5. After successful transaction you will receive payment id, order id and signature.




	Note.

	In this integration, we have coverd below point
	1. Dynamic order creation
	2. Payment signature verification
	3. Fetch payment api
	4. We are storing all parameter retured from fetch payment api into database.
  5. Developer can customize can as per their requirement
